column187: Being able to afford certain things can depend on salary but can also depend on other factors, perhaps a person has rich parents or perhaps they've inherited a large sum of money. Being able to afford rich things doesn't necessarily relate to a higher salary. Acting the part you want, i.e., dressing for the job you want, is a factor but doing things like renting a penthouse apartment to appear better than you are is a waste of money that he hasn't got yet.
